[77.427282, "o", "  UTC:    2024-03-31 08:00:00 UTC\r\n"]
[77.427313, "o", "  Berlin: 2024-03-31 10:00:00 CEST (UTC+0200)\r\n\r\n"]
[77.427341, "o", "Meeting: Maintenance Window Prep\r\n  UTC:    2024-03-31 01:30:00 UTC\r\n"]
[77.42737, "o", "  Berlin: 2024-03-31 03:30:00 CEST (UTC+0200)\r\n\r\nMeeting: Weekly Review\r\n"]
[77.427397, "o", "  UTC:    2024-04-01 14:00:00 UTC\r\n  Berlin: 2024-04-01 16:00:00 CEST (UTC+0200)\r\n\r\n"]
[77.427422, "o", "Meeting: Client Call\r\n  UTC:    2024-03-30 15:30:00 UTC\r\n"]
[77.427455, "o", "  Berlin: 2024-03-30 16:30:00 CET (UTC+0100)\r\n\r\nMeeting: Team Lunch\r\n"]
[77.427485, "o", "  UTC:    2024-03-29 11:00:00 UTC\r\n  Berlin: 2024-03-29 12:00:00 CET (UTC+0100)\r\n\r\n============================================================\r\nKey finding for 'Maintenance Window Prep':\r\n  UTC time: 2024-03-31T01:30:00\r\n"]
[77.427514, "o", "  This is during DST transition (2am CET -> 3am CEST)\r\n  Correct Berlin time: 2024-03-31 03:30:00 CEST\r\n  (The 2am hour is skipped due to DST transition)\r\n============================================================\r\n"]
[77.431849, "o", "\u001b[?2004h"]
[77.431885, "o", "user@e252a997ef07:~/scheduler$ "]
[93.020983, "i", "cat > BUGFIX_SUMMARY.txt << 'EOF'\n=================================================================\nBUGFIX SUMMARY: Timezone Conversion Issue in Meeting Scheduler\n=================================================================\n\nPROBLEM:\n--------\nThe scheduler app was sending meeting reminders at incorrect times,\nspecifically for meetings falling between 2am-3am local time during\nDST transitions. The offset was exactly 1 hour.\n\nROOT CAUSE:\n-----------\nIn app.py, the convert_to_berlin() function was incorrectly using:\n  BERLIN_TZ.localize(utc_dt)\n\nThis treated the UTC datetime as if it were already in Berlin time,\nrather than converting FROM UTC TO Berlin time.\n\nDuring DST transitions (like March 31, 2024 when clocks jump from\n2am CET to 3am CEST), this caused incorrect time calculations.\n\nEXAMPLE:\n--------\nMaintenance Window Prep meeting:\n  Stored as:     2024-03-31T01:30:00 UTC\n  \n  OLD (BUGGY):   2024-03-31 01:30:00 CET (UTC+0100)\n                 [Incorrectly treats UTC time as Berlin time]\n  \n  NEW (FIXE"]
[93.021098, "i", "D):   2024-03-31 03:30:00 CEST (UTC+0200)\n                 [Correctly converts UTC to Berlin time]\n  \n  Difference:    1 hour off (would send reminder at wrong time)\n\nSOLUTION:\n---------\nFixed the convert_to_berlin() function to properly:\n1. Parse the UTC time string\n2. Localize it as UTC using UTC_TZ.localize(utc_dt)\n3. Convert to Berlin time using utc_dt.astimezone(BERLIN_TZ)\n\nCODE CHANGE:\n------------\n- OLD: berlin_dt = BERLIN_TZ.localize(utc_dt)\n+ NEW: utc_dt = UTC_TZ.localize(utc_dt)\n+      berlin_dt = utc_dt.astimezone(BERLIN_TZ)\n\nVERIFICATION:\n-------------\n- Fixed code now correctly handles DST transitions\n- All meetings convert to proper Berlin local time\n- Cron job will now send reminders at correct times\n- No changes needed to crontab or meetings.json\n\nFILES MODIFIED:\n---------------\n- /home/user/scheduler/app.py (fixed convert_to_berlin function)\n- /home/user/scheduler/app.py.backup (backup of original buggy version)\n\n=================================================================\nEOF\n"]
[93.021182, "o", "cat > BUGFIX_SUMMARY.txt << 'EOF'\r\n"]
